WEBVTT

00:06:57.080 --> 00:07:00.576
Because when enough people care enough,

00:07:00.600 --> 00:07:04.176
the politicians, most of whom
won't lead on this issue --

00:07:04.200 --> 00:07:05.976
but they will be led --

00:07:06.000 --> 00:07:07.376
that will change this.

00:07:07.400 --> 00:07:11.456
Because I can tell you,
the ice doesn't care.

00:07:11.480 --> 00:07:13.896
The ice doesn't care
who's in the White House.

00:07:13.920 --> 00:07:16.896
It doesn't care which party
controls your congress.

00:07:16.920 --> 00:07:19.496
It doesn't care which party
controls your parliament.

00:07:19.520 --> 00:07:20.976
It just melts.

00:07:21.000 --> 00:07:22.216
Thank you very much.

00:07:22.240 --> 00:07:28.160
(Applause)